N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 30.1 - Fleet

State Regulations
A fleet shall be a minimum number of vehicles determined by
the commissioner. The fleet registrations may be passenger, commercial, trailers, special purpose commercial in any combination. Notes
